---
import { SITE_AUTHOR, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
const today = new Date();
---
<footer>
  <div class="site-shell footer-inner">
    <div class="footer-brand">
      <strong>{SITE_TITLE}</strong>
      <p>ETF低吸、高抛、复盘与验证。</p>
    </div>
    <nav class="footer-links" aria-label="页脚导航">
      <a href="/garden">今日推荐</a>
      <a href="/blog">每日复盘</a>
      <a href="/momentum/">A股雷达</a>
      <a href="/us-garden/">美股ETF花园</a>
      <a href="/us-momentum/">美股雷达</a>
      <a href="/research">策略研究</a>
      <a href="/garden/history">花园历史</a>
      <a href="/about">方法说明</a>
      <a href="/rss.xml">RSS订阅</a>
      <a href="/token">工具</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
  <div class="site-shell disclaimer">本站仅用于个人研究和策略复盘，不构成投资建议。数据可能延迟、缺失或错误；历史表现不代表未来收益，交易风险由使用者自行承担。</div>
  <div class="site-shell copyright">© {today.getFullYear()} {SITE_AUTHOR} · 个人研究记录</div>
</footer>
<style>
  footer { padding: 2.2rem 0 3.2rem; color: rgb(var(--gray)); background: var(--warm); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .footer-inner { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1.5rem; }
  footer strong { color: rgb(var(--black)); }
  footer p { margin: 0.3rem 0 0; font-size: 0.88rem; }
  .footer-links { display: flex; max-width: 600px; gap: 0.45rem 0.9rem; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: flex-end; }
  .footer-links a { color: rgb(var(--gray-dark)); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.86rem; font-weight: 750; }
  .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  .copyright { margin-top: 1.35rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgb(var(--gray)); }
  .disclaimer { margin-top: 1.35rem; padding: 0.85rem 1rem; border-radius: 12px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.48); border: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 0.78rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .disclaimer + .copyright { margin-top: 0.7rem; }
  @media (max-width: 720px) { .footer-inner { flex-direction: column; } .footer-links { justify-content: flex-start; } }
</style>
